nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:
<a modern building with a unique architectural design (Salmani Style). The building is a three-story structure plus the ground floor with a flat roof and large windows on the upper level.>

<Left Facade><
1- The windows are arranged in a grid-like pattern, having a greenish color. 

2- The exterior of the building is made up of a big, visible, beige and brown brick cladding. The brickwork includes a variety of patterns and textures, creating visual interest and depth, while the glass elements provide transparency and a connection to the outdoors.

3- The facade has protruding horizontal strips of greenish granite cladding installed on the two bording lines of the exterior facade. The granite material reacts with light showing the roughness of it and with the way it reflects light, the green color of the granite is harmonic with the rest of the scene and matches with the other colors of ther facade.>

<Right Facade><

1- the windows are pvc type windows made of aluminum and green glass.

2- The wall is beige stucco painted with a shade of color close to brick cladding in the left facade.>

<General scene><

1- On the right side of the image, there is a large tree with green leaves, and on the left side, there are two silver, Porsche cars passing by the sidewalk . The sky is blue with a few white clouds scattered across it. The street is made of asphalt material with street curbs on the perimeter of it. The image appears to be taken from a low angle, looking up at the building.

2- The photo is captured in a sunny, daytime architectural visualization, Lens flare and people motion blur.

3- The overall composition emphasizes a blend of contemporary design and traditional materials, creating a harmonious environment conducive to working and collaboration.>

nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:
A modern office building, featuring a ground floor and three upper levels. It consistes of two facades.

Left Facade:

The left facade includes vertical green-tinted glass columns between textured beige sandstone walls with a rough and natural finish. 

rough, high-quality stone—not irregular.

The glass reflects the blue sky and surrounding structures.

The left facade has two polished, green marble cladding located in the horizontal borders of the left facade, both are protruded from finish level of the left facade one just above the ground floor in the left facade and one at the roofline of the left facade, catching direct sunlight with subtle reflections.

Right Facade:

Aluminum-framed windows with green-tinted glazing.

Beige stucco wall texture, roughly finished and slightly warm-toned.

Scene:

one luxury silver Porsche car passing on a rough asphalt street with curbs.

A lush green tree on the right side of the image.

People walking near the building, slightly motion-blurred.

Captured from a low-angle perspective.

Bright, sunny day with a clear blue sky, soft white clouds, and lens flare.

Sun positioned high (approx. 80° altitude), casting crisp shadows and enhancing the building’s form.

Atmosphere:

Emphasis on contemporary elegance and traditional materials blended in a clean, professional architectural visualization.

widgets_values:
A modern office building in Salmani architectural style, featuring a ground floor and three upper levels and consists of two façades. The left facade includes vertical green-tinted glass columns between textured beige sandstone walls with a rough and natural finish.

Left Façade:

(The left facade has two polished, green marble cladding located in the horizontal borders of the left facade, both are protruded from the left facade, one strip is above the ground floor in the left facade and one strip is at the roofline of the left facade, catching direct sunlight with subtle reflections. Avoid green marble cladding on all areas except the far-left and far-right edges of the left façade; exclude green marble from central sections, right façade, roof, and ground floor; no green marble on window frames or middle columns; prevent green marble from appearing on unintended surfaces.:7.45)

Vertical rhythmic divisions with tall green glass sections framed in beige sandstone.

Smooth, high-quality stone—not blocky or irregular.

The glass reflects the blue sky and surrounding structures.

Right Façade:

Aluminum-framed windows with dark green-tinted glazing.

Beige stucco wall texture, smoothly finished and slightly warm-toned.

Scene:

Two luxury silver Porsche cars passing on a smooth asphalt street with curbs.

A lush green tree on the right side of the image.

People walking near the building, slightly motion-blurred.

Captured from a low-angle perspective.

Bright, sunny day with a clear blue sky, soft white clouds, and lens flare.

Sun positioned high (approx. 80° altitude), casting crisp shadows and enhancing the building’s form.

Atmosphere:

Emphasis on contemporary elegance and traditional materials blended in a clean, professional architectural visualization.

A highly detailed, cinematic exterior night shot of a modern rectangular commercial building, masterpiece quality. The building has a flat concrete roof with a low-profile mechanical unit centered at the top. The symmetrical facade is divided into six equal storefronts:

The four central sections are clad in textured sandstone and large, dark blue reflective, transparent glass panels, revealing subtle glimpses of illuminated interiors.

The leftmost section is (clad in textured gray basalt:3.5).

The rightmost section is (finished in rough white stucco:2.05), visibly textured.

Each storefront is marked at the top by a purple diamond-shaped with the number of the store inside in bold white letters this area is finished with dark blue non-transparent glass. A clean horizontal white store sign is in every section. The base of each section features dark blue reflective glass panels that offer transparent views into the softly lit interiors, emphasizing (interior light glow and night ambiance:8).

two red rectangular boxes with pink triangle symbols—possibly logos—are mounted on the lower sections of tw different storefronts. The rough, light-colored concrete ground in front of the building reflects ambient light.
